  <entry align="center">Attibute Name</entry>
  <entry align="center">Description</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry>perfSONAR_DAEMONS</entry>
<entry>
If true, Enable perfSONAR owampd and bwctld daemons. Otherwise disable 
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>perfSONAR_BWCTLD </entry>
<entry>
